export function Flooter(){
    return <flooter style={{
    position: "fixed",
    height: "40px",
    width: "100%",
    backgroundColor: "gray",
    zIndex: "80",
    bottom: "0",
    fontSize: "22px",
    lineHeight: "40px",
    fontWeight: "800",
    color: "white",
    textAlign: "center",
    borderTop: "5px inset rgb(238, 226, 226, 0.5)"
    }}
    >網 石__版 權 所 有__2021
    </flooter>
}
